1. Part 907_Navel Oranges Grown in Arizona and Designated Part of California is removed. 


PART 908_[REMOVED]


2. Part 908_Valencia Oranges Grown in Arizona and 
Designated Part of California is removed. 


PART 910_[REMOVED]


3. Part 910_Lemons Grown in California and Arizona is removed.



