This SFAR may be used, at the agency's discretion, in enforcement actions involving individuals presenting dangerous
or deadly weapons for screening at airports or in checked baggage where the amount of the proposed civil penalty is
less than $5,000. In these cases,   13.16(a), 13.16(c), and 13.16(f) through (l) of this chapter are used,
as well as sections (A) through (D) below:


 

