63. 

Discussion.

 We believe that, in order to prevent the delay in bringing service to the public that might be occasioned by bankruptcies
or by prolonged financial negotiations, it is important to require licensee to have the financial ability to construct
and operate a system in addition to being able to purchase the license. Consequently we will continue to require applicants
